trialdata.stimulus:
Get ready to start the game!

Thank you for reading the instructions. Get ready start with the first of 5 block(s) of this game.

In this first block, you will complete 90 rounds of this game before moving on.

Remember, the better you perform, the bigger your bonus will be!

Press space to begin.

End of block!

You have reached the end of the block 1/5. If you need a short break, feel free to take one now before moving on.

In the next block, you will complete another 90 rounds of this game.
